{"tid":2506522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"林家棟同古天樂爭風呷醋 逼問試當真Locker二揀一","createTime":"2021-04-27T11:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T11:32:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"143db97261d979b0f844579d6a45859cd0353f52","tid":2506522,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/AqNQ_pjSKJB8NdB72NglsZateg0=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SWVPMCOLI5CM3NS4KO4KWIPBRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FAqNQ_pjSKJB8NdB72NglsZateg0%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSWVPMCOLI5CM3NS4KO4KWIPBRE.jpg&h=fd21dc21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n疫情緩和，戲院重開，電影業再見曙光，古天樂與林家棟合作的新片《惡行之外》近日開鏡，由新導演郭文奇執導，邀來張繼聰、王敏奕、車婉婉、孫佳君及一班新演員林家熙（Locker）、楊偲泳、林婷、陳紫萱、鄧月平等演出，還有林嘉欣特別客串一角。<br />\n<br />\n古天樂、林家棟上次合作演拍檔，今次分別飾演父親，各自為子女的生死展開搏鬥，古仔表示：「今次我為個女報仇，家棟就為個仔擋，勢成水火。」<br />\n<br />\n而YouTube頻道「試當真」的骨幹成員Locker，戲中飾演林家棟與車婉婉的兒子，今次與兩個同門師妹楊偲泳、林婷一同演出，Locker說：「好彩我哋幾個本來都好熟，已私下溝通為角色劇本做定功課。」Locker表示非常感激老闆古天樂給新人機會，在旁的家棟即帶笑逼問Locker：「老竇緊要，定係老闆緊要？」Locker識趣回答當然是老竇最重要。<br />\n<br />\n至於首次拍戲演古仔女兒的林婷坦言，以前總覺得古天樂好cool，接觸之後發覺他比想像中善良與親民。張繼聰、王敏奕被問到有否興趣自薦唱主題曲，他們笑說：「有『我最喜愛的男歌手』喺度，點同古仔爭呀？除非有5、6首插曲，我哋先有機會分到一小段唱吓！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Vx9_pfMCN76Fydfwdu9Aox0A4HY=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FWX3EM6IL5F6RAMOEU6WVEORQU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVx9_pfMCN76Fydfwdu9Aox0A4HY%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFWX3EM6IL5F6RAMOEU6WVEORQU.JPG&h=7f27f977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/znXiZpIVhshe_DeaUFpKwcQ-FSA=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RVXI6RRDR5HXJMFZAMYQYDTEEY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FznXiZpIVhshe_DeaUFpKwcQ-FSA%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRVXI6RRDR5HXJMFZAMYQYDTEEY.JPG&h=8ff50b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_AX_hfeELlsEMl4Z3fScj-HMJM0=/802x1203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5QQJRZ43LVFZLAXDDX2PTFSUUE.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_AX_hfeELlsEMl4Z3fScj-HMJM0%3D%2F802x1203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5QQJRZ43LVFZLAXDDX2PTFSUUE.jpeg&h=686e1950&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wRVOp7fkogVZaBvdRvOTAj40YK0=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OCAWCVMTPJFYVHKNXYJCCXW4Q4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwRVOp7fkogVZaBvdRvOTAj40YK0%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOCAWCVMTPJFYVHKNXYJCCXW4Q4.jpeg&h=86d3d56a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/so75anet7SkJVuIuOJvuW309Ycc=/802x1203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TPBEECVMLNF4RGTDKQTT2HC6W4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fso75anet7SkJVuIuOJvuW309Ycc%3D%2F802x1203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTPBEECVMLNF4RGTDKQTT2HC6W4.jpeg&h=402fa2a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mp4TZfgc73OAWiHh4AVW62_5ibo=/802x534/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4HQGNZYXXZGRPBCKWTP67XO46E.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fmp4TZfgc73OAWiHh4AVW62_5ibo%3D%2F802x534%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4HQGNZYXXZGRPBCKWTP67XO46E.JPG&h=9a098f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210427/X5DKW45UR5H7RHXYRFPYDSNGBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210427%2FX5DKW45UR5H7RHXYRFPYDSNGBM%2F&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oCwbHaueoKb2XZOoGTcnCr8%3D&h=0ebc1fe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210427%2FX5DKW45UR5H7RHXYRFPYDSNGBM%2F&h=32ab1ab2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210427/X5DKW45UR5H7RHXYRFPYDSNGBM/</a>"},{"pid":"42b925c6c86a0aac99879739dfab345d2fcc4605","tid":2506522,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"支持..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33069e02675b41485fcce8979fd037d65edc71f2","tid":2506522,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"鄧月平咩版本"},{"pid":"c75bfe180a0c57b3d1c576f518bab388785dafbd","tid":2506522,"uid":190789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:14:07.000Z","msg":"古天樂真係有心"},{"pid":"2d2d09640d51f706683a7ac266fbd45fc5ef3ce8","tid":2506522,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42b925c6c86a0aac99879739dfab345d2fcc4605","tid":2506522,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"支持..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T11:16:58.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":